as\\Ncon pre-PMF:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"- Menor Hb","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"- Menor recuento plaquetario","guid":"hpjPMXXzNC0ap2zeQtfCZQ","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"- Mayor número de blastos circulantes","guid":"wbhKm2nYqxXwxH4gYSMbIA","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"- Mayor frecuencia y gravedad de síntomas constitucionales","guid":"Y6VBN4ZcR0CW7SqTwouMlA","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"177","text":"- Mayor esplenomegalia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"170","text":"- Modelos pronósticos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"- GIPSS (basado exclusivamente en mutaciones y cariotipo)","guid":"wTf0ByJMCwKZK_GeM1GCdg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"- MIPSS70+ versión 2.0 (factores genéticos y clínicos)","guid":"UK8sGG_bk_1ymIx-cjDbLA","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"170","text":"- Riesgo de\\Ntransformación a fase\\Nblástica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"- Pre-PMF: 7% a 5 años, 12% a 10 años","guid":"CjE8v8swIqpiIYeHgilQpQ","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"- PMF manifiesto: 11% a 5 años, 23% a 10 años","guid":"KC1hs7uDP8TSTRL5ii5lAw","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"- Factores de riesgo: mutaciones IDH1/ASXL1/SRSF2, cariotipo de muy alto riesgo, edad >70 años,\\Nsexo masculino, blastos circulantes >3%, anemia moderada o grave, síntomas constitucionales","guid":"wcHgFRsijGq4l4ow_ni7wQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"170","text":"- Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"- Adaptado al riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"- Riesgo bajo/muy bajo: observación","guid":"7OKz9Y9vWIQ7YNXeBzM96A","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"- Riesgo alto/muy alto: trasplante de células madre alogénicas","guid":"5RNoV0Yhi5ReuaKWah7u9A","children":[]},{"id":"194","